  "title": "Construction Legal Counsel - Construction Firm | Jurong - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position title : Construction Legal Counsel</strong></p><ul><li>Location: Jurong</li><li>Working Days: Monday- Friday, 5 days</li><li>Working hours : 8am to 530pm</li><li>Salary :  Up to $5,500</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Draft, review and negotiate contracts, agreements and other documents; and render legal advice</li><li>Provide legal advice and support to the group of companies on a broad range of commercial issues</li><li>Handle the setting up of subsidiaries, associates, branches and project offices as well as the closing or liquidation of such set up</li><li>Coordinate with external legal counsels and consultants as well as oversee the progress of their work</li><li>Coordinate with and advise business units and departments on legal matters</li><li>Any other duties to be assigned from time to time</li></ul><p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Law</li><li>4 to 7 years’ post-qualification experience, <strong>with knowledge of construction law </strong>and/or with experience in the <strong>construction industry</strong></li><li>Willing to travel when required</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, WA your resume to ‪‪‪‪‪‪‪‪+65 9136 9792‬‬‬‬‬‬‬‬ or email your resume to supreme.yentan@gmail.com.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
